headline: MGIC Investment Shares Gain 2.3% as Q2 Earnings Top Estimates
summary: MTG beats Q2 EPS estimates by 17.1% as new insurance written jumps 21.5% and net premiums rise year over year.

headline: Radian Group Q2 Earnings Top Estimates, Premiums Decline Y/Y
